{"tid":16123,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[直播推到完場] 20:00 ABL常規賽 - 高雄聖徒@東方龍獅","createTime":"2016-12-01T10:09:14.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-07T12:51:37.000Z","uid":9030,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a5434cd72836eeea03ea4ebddb400d53e4f1db83","tid":16123,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T10:09:14.000Z","msg":"cable app免費直播<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2d590d555bc11165cbc9dc0ad31022ae537a759","tid":16123,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T10:11:39.000Z","msg":"【東南亞職籃】東方龍獅即出戰　粉絲修頓搶飛<br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=zBKsoIV%2FeLhWSsP5H2J%2BmmN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=01bb4806\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】 香港首次舉辦東南亞職業聯賽，東方龍獅首次主場，不但吸引一班平日熱愛本地籃球的球迷撐場，更吸引到新fans！今晚8點東方龍獅將會在灣仔修頓室內場館迎戰高雄聖徒，加上今次波飛開售時間推前到中午12點，最早到場排隊的球迷，9點半已經到達修頓。排頭幾位的文先生表示：「自己之前沒有看過本地籃球，只有入場看過學界，今次知道東方龍獅打東南亞職業聯賽，所以入場支持香港球隊。」<br />\n為打造東方龍獅主場氣勢，在開賣前球隊市場部已經著手佈置修頓場館，兩旁的走道都有球員大型banner，門口亦有橫額寫上「東方龍獅場館」，十分有心思。"},{"pid":"d00bf6fdec22dadbe55de9dee8baa8a70d2ebabb","tid":16123,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T10:16:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20161201/photo/bkn-20161201113241415-1201_00882_001_02b.jpg?20161201150621\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20161201%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20161201113241415-1201_00882_001_02b.jpg%3F20161201150621&h=b894b407&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c26cb9d3486231bef66ce5e5ed19bb525d15b02d","tid":16123,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T10:17:33.000Z","msg":"東方龍獅今晚就會返到主場修頓，出戰在晚上八時舉行的東南亞職業聯賽（ABL），面對周日以90：79擊敗過的高雄聖徒。<br />\n<br />\n門票於今午12時開售，排頭位的約九時半已經到達球場門外排隊，大約有30名球迷排隊。排在第三位的文先生在早上10時就排隊，他指以往都很少看本地籃球，更是首次入場看甲一球隊的賽事，平時都只看NBA，對東方亦不太認識，這次是與朋友和同事湊熱鬧入場看比賽。<br />\n東方在早上已經到修頓進行最後一次的訓練，而高雄聖徒就緊接東方之後到場練習。大會人員已經馬不停蹄地在場外進行佈置工作，亦在修頓門外拉起「東方龍獅場館」的橫額，比高雄的場館更有氣勢。"},{"pid":"dbe972e61e5c11604e10372eda64d75c453e6942","tid":16123,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T10:23:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/4ywlfkab\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F4ywlfkab&h=caa768e1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7faed25bcbdbe753c25a1d4059b116dab93d74e7","tid":16123,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T10:28:26.000Z","msg":"十卜狗志"},{"pid":"42fce22512e12a78d7f8021c32c22d03f00aa5ff","tid":16123,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T10:46:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>十卜狗志</blockquote><br />\nfor the good of hong kong"},{"pid":"5ce1fb1da8bdd79ca96163dbd6afb4f104b841ae","tid":16123,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T11:12:56.000Z","msg":"好大機會full house"},{"pid":"6e96d8539f777081b57b792c8bc87a079c8245ab","tid":16123,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T11:36:51.000Z","msg":"live: <a href=\"http://www.i-cable.com/liveabl/live_ch62.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.i-cable.com%2Fliveabl%2Flive_ch62.php&d=zBKsoIV%2FeLhWSsP5H2J%2BmmN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=f29d9a08\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.i-cable.com/liveabl/live_ch62.php</a>"},{"pid":"eb6e8cb6e470ebfa3e40860f04e84f969886f2a9","tid":16123,"uid":30294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T11:44:02.000Z","msg":"my fd今日入左場???"},{"pid":"119df273785b591372c4e43e259c1ea7b9ea4201","tid":16123,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T11:46:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>my fd今日入左場???</blockquote><br />\n冇入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 忙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n7號應該入"},{"pid":"410029a21328dbe9ccf70260964a28640